		{"id":"phase2-note","type":"text","text":"⭐ **Flagship: Negotiation**\n\nTwo LLM agents (Priya + Rajesh) negotiate in real multi-round dialogue with separate prompts, hidden floor prices, and private reasoning.\n\nEach round saved as structured data + natural language message.\n\nOn deal acceptance → auto-creates Purchase Order + logs 2 events on chain.","x":540,"y":-220,"width":320,"height":320,"color":"3"},
