		{"id":"contract","type":"text","text":"## Smart Contract\n\n**`SupplyChainAudit.sol`**\nSepolia: `0x...`\n\nStores fingerprints:\n- `referenceId` (bytes32)\n- `eventType` (uint8)\n- `documentHash` (bytes32)\n- `amount` (uint256)\n- `timestamp`\n- `submittedBy`\n\n~80K gas per event.","x":180,"y":720,"width":280,"height":280,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"sepolia","type":"text","text":"## ⛓️ Ethereum Sepolia\n\nPractice version of Ethereum.\n\nFree test ETH from faucets.\nReal confirmation ~30s.\n\nCost per event: **~$0.0003**\n\nAll txs visible on Etherscan.","x":500,"y":720,"width":280,"height":280,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"stack","type":"text","text":"## 🏗️ Tech Stack\n\n**Frontend:** Next.js 16, Tailwind, shadcn/ui, React Query, Zustand\n**Backend:** Express 5, TypeScript, MongoDB, JWT\n**AI:** Mastra AI 1.4, Google Gemini 2.0 Flash\n**Blockchain:** Hardhat, Solidity 0.8.24, ethers.js 6\n**DB:** MongoDB Atlas\n**LLM:** Gemini 2.0 Flash","x":-440,"y":1080,"width":880,"height":180,"color":"3"},
